org.block.panel.block

Interface Block.CalledBlock

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Block
    Enclosing interface:
    Block

    public static interface Block.CalledBlock
extends Block
    If your code requires calls to be added into the output code project, then this should be implemented. Please note, if two callables are found to have the same name with the same parameters/location then an exception will be thrown when outputting the code (This is not a good thing)
